text = "December 20th 
Today was very eventful. It always is with rosaline. Never have I thought being a mother would bring me such joy. But when I look at Roseline’s mesmerizing purple eyes, feelings of love and warmth overcome me. Gerald on the other hand has just been a big grump. He says he’s worried about me. I keep telling him that I’m not pregnant anymore but he won’t have it. Sometimes I wonder what I saw in him. 

The rest of the book is filled with Lilian's and Rosaline's activities on a daily basis... 
"
