text = "July 26th
For the past 4 months, Lilian has been leaving the house to go to the town a lot more. She's never told me what she was going to do there but I just guessed maybe she made some friends over there. I didn't want to stop her either, because since she started going there, there has been no talk of ‘Roseline’. But things changed since I saw her talking to the prince. Everyone and their mothers’ know that you didn’t want your female relative talking to him. Because most times they would end up being one of his many girlfriends. So imagine my surprise when I saw him talking to my wife! Not only that but, I was also surprised to see him talking to my wife. And worse of it they seemed to be flirting! The prince may be a dangerous man but when it comes to protecting my wife from scum like him, I am even more dangerous."
